{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3c689f96-58ee-4813-87fd-80659ef544a7","content":"No pipeline files found in the repo, so here's a general migration guide.\n\n## Migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n### 1. Update your test project\n\nIn each test `.csproj`, add:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 2. Replace `VSTest@3` with `dotnet test`\n\n**Before (VSTest@3):**\n```yaml\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**\\*Tests.dll'\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n    resultFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)\\TestResults\n```\n\n**After (`dotnet test` with Microsoft.Testing.Platform):**\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=testresults.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish TRX results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key differences\n\n| Concern | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Runner | vstest.console | Test host is the exe itself |\n| TRX reports | Built-in | `--logger trx` |\n| Code coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Result publish | Automatic | Needs `PublishTestResults@2` |\n\n> **Tip:** If you use Coverlet instead of the built-in collector, replace `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` with `--collect:\"XPlat Code Coverage\"` and the summary will already be Cobertura XML.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2602c7fe-e50c-4e11-b2cb-5342ec31c2f5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"No pipeline files found. The user is asking a general question about migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in Azure DevOps pipelines. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":657,"requestId":"E3FD:17DD88:1692019:192D262:6A052003"},"id":"3b4a231b-5c8a-473b-8642-4716d09c25af","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:06:23.864Z","parentId":"8b8788e5-45ba-4b7c-92e8-04a1977b337f"}
